.stripeform_container
    .text-red-darkest.text-center.mb-10.-mt-5.text-lg.font-semibold.leading-tight
        Thank you for your interest! Become a subscriber for a meager 100sek to enjoy all the latest news,
        be able to comment on articles, and get updates on our fantastic partner offers.

    = form_with url: subscribers_path, local: true, id: 'subscriber_form' do |form|
        = form.label 'Credit or debit card'
        %br/
        = form.label '100 SEK'

        #card-element.border-2.rounded-full.m-4.ml-32.mr-32.p-2.bg-grey-lightest
            
        .mb-32= form.submit 'Submit Payment'